  "name": "Handle Animal",
  "type": "feat",
  "img": "systems/pf1/icons/items/inventory/lockpick.jpg",
  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<strong>Unchained Rogue Skill Unlock</strong><br/><br/><p>With sufficient ranks in Handle Animal, you earn the following.</p><p><b>5 Ranks: </b>Creatures you have trained gain a +2 bonus on Will saves when adjacent to you.</p><p><b>10 Ranks: </b>Creatures you have trained gain a +2 bonus on Will saves whenever you are within 30 feet and clearly visible. You can teach a trick in 1 day by increasing the DC by 20.</p><p><b>15 Ranks: </b>You can train an animal to understand your speech (as speak with animals) with 1 week of effort and a successful DC 30 Handle Animal check. Its actions are still limited by its Intelligence. You can teach a trick in 1 day (increasing the DC by 10) or 1 hour (increasing the DC by 20).</p><p><b>20 Ranks: </b>You can make your speech understandable to any animal for 24 hours with a successful DC 30 Handle Animal check (DC 40 for magical beasts or vermin). You can teach a trick in 1 day, 1 hour (increasing the DC by 10), or 1 minute (increasing the DC by 20).</p>",
